>>We'll learn about why we need DNS and how it works. 
>>We'll also show you why DHCP makes network administration a simpler task.


By the end of this module,

>>you'll be able to do describe how DNS and DHCP work, 
>>how NAT technologies help keep networks secure, and 
>>how VPNs and proxies help users connect and stay secured.
